Detailed Description

cvmx_tdec::_tc_error_mask_reg

This register enables internal decoder errors. Errors reported in TDEC()_TC_ERROR_REG will generate an error signal only when the corresponding bit is set in TDEC()_TC_ERROR_REG[ERR_MASK].
